msgid "Change 4.23.0 above to whatever version you want installed."
msgstr "Změňte 4.23.0 výše na libovolnou verzi, kterou chcete nainstalovat."

#: download/linux.html:127
msgid "Manual binary install"
msgstr "Ruční binární instalace"

#: download/linux.html:128
#, python-format
msgid ""
"If you wish to revert to an earlier calibre release or download a calibre "
